	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Sure "reproductions" of anything are possible.
<br />
<br />For same mapper multicarts it's easy, you just need a lot of 8-bit memory and to allocate a little space on the program ROM to store the menu.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
