	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />NES emulators do support pirate multicarts and their strange mappers, so I guess the roms are available somewhere
<br />
<br />You will have to re-create the mapper yourself, but it is usually made of simple chips. See Kevtris's site for more info <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.kevtris.org/">http://www.kevtris.org/</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />droppingsload???  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
